title: Silent Hill 0rigins playthrough — Part 1
description: This skips the intro because I played it already a couple times. Had to stop before because the graphics were messed up and I didn't know why, but now it's fixed. Game is pretty cool. Kind of a basic SH game. A lot like 3 but with more exploration and worse controls.
